These bankers run the Farming Guild branch of the Bank of Gielinor, located in the north section of the guild. Level 85 Farming is required to access them, though there is a bank chest in the guild available at 45 Farming.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The female banker is identical to Elena Hosidius, and the male banker is identical to Hans.
